body:
# SeqTools
Tools for manipulating sequences in F#, based on the Python module [itertools](https://docs.python.org/3/library/itertools.html)

Including:

- count
- cycle
- repeat
- accumulate
- chain
- compress
- product
- permutations
- combinations
- combinationsWithReplacement
